{"title": "Nmap", "source": "enum", "source_label": "Enumeration", "path": "nmap", "html": "<h1 id=\"nmap\">Nmap</h1>\n<h2 id=\"host-discovery\">Host Discovery</h2>\n<div class=\"highlight\"><pre><span></span><code><span class=\"c1\"># Ping sweep (no port scan)</span>\nnmap<span class=\"w\"> </span>-sn<span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"m\">192</span>.168.1.0/24\n\n<span class=\"c1\"># ARP discovery (local network, requires root)</span>\nnmap<span class=\"w\"> </span>-PR<span class=\"w\"> </span>-sn<span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"m\">192</span>.168.1.0/24\n\n<span class=\"c1\"># TCP SYN ping</span>\nnmap<span class=\"w\"> </span>-PS22,80,443<span class=\"w\"> </span>-sn<span class=\"w\"> </span>&lt;ip&gt;\n\n<span class=\"c1\"># UDP ping</span>\nnmap<span class=\"w\"> </span>-PU53,161<span class=\"w\"> </span>-sn<span class=\"w\"> </span>&lt;ip&gt;\n\n<span class=\"c1\"># ICMP echo + timestamp + netmask</span>\nnmap<span class=\"w\"> </span>-PE<span class=\"w\"> </span>-PP<span class=\"w\"> </span>-PM<span class=\"w\"> </span>-sn<span class=\"w\"> </span>&lt;ip&gt;\n\n<span class=\"c1\"># No ping (treat host as up)</span>\nnmap<span class=\"w\"> </span>-Pn<span class=\"w\"> </span>&lt;ip&gt;\n\n<span class=\"c1\"># Disable DNS resolution</span>\nnmap<span class=\"w\"> </span>-n<span class=\"w\"> </span>-sn<span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"m\">192</span>.168.1.0/24\n\n<span class=\"c1\"># List targets without scanning</span>\nnmap<span class=\"w\"> </span>-sL<span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"m\">192</span>.168.1.0/24\n</code></pre></div>\n<h2 id=\"port-scanning-tcp\">Port Scanning — TCP</h2>\n<div class=\"highlight\"><pre><span></span><code><span class=\"c1\"># SYN scan (default, requires root)</span>\nnmap<span class=\"w\"> </span>-sS<span class=\"w\"> </span>&lt;ip&gt;\n\n<span class=\"c1\"># Full TCP connect scan (no root needed)</span>\nnmap<span class=\"w\"> </span>-sT<span class=\"w\"> </span>&lt;ip&gt;\n\n<span class=\"c1\"># All ports</span>\nnmap<span class=\"w\"> </span>-sS<span class=\"w\"> </span>-p-<span class=\"w\"> </span>&lt;ip&gt;\n\n<span class=\"c1\"># Top 1000 ports (default)</span>\nnmap<span class=\"w\"> </span>-sS<span class=\"w\"> </span>&lt;ip&gt;\n\n<span class=\"c1\"># Top N ports</span>\nnmap<span class=\"w\"> </span>--top-ports<span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"m\">100</span><span class=\"w\"> </span>&lt;ip&gt;\n\n<span class=\"c1\"># Specific ports</span>\nnmap<span class=\"w\"> </span>-p<span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"m\">22</span>,80,443,8080,8443<span class=\"w\"> </span>&lt;ip&gt;\n\n<span class=\"c1\"># Port range</span>\nnmap<span class=\"w\"> </span>-p<span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"m\">1</span>-65535<span class=\"w\"> </span>&lt;ip&gt;\n\n<span class=\"c1\"># HTB/CTF standard full scan</span>\nnmap<span class=\"w\"> </span>-sCV<span class=\"w\"> </span>-T4<span class=\"w\"> </span>--min-rate<span class=\"o\">=</span><span class=\"m\">1000</span><span class=\"w\"> </span>-p-<span class=\"w\"> </span>&lt;ip&gt;\n\n<span class=\"c1\"># Fast initial scan then full</span>\nnmap<span class=\"w\"> </span>-sS<span class=\"w\"> </span>--top-ports<span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"m\">1000</span><span class=\"w\"> </span>&lt;ip&gt;<span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"o\">&amp;&amp;</span><span class=\"w\"> </span>nmap<span class=\"w\"> </span>-sS<span class=\"w\"> </span>-p-<span class=\"w\"> </span>&lt;ip&gt;\n</code></pre></div>\n<h2 id=\"port-scanning-udp\">Port Scanning — UDP</h2>\n<div class=\"highlight\"><pre><span></span><code><span class=\"c1\"># UDP scan (slow, requires root)</span>\nnmap<span class=\"w\"> </span>-sU<span class=\"w\"> </span>&lt;ip&gt;\n\n<span class=\"c1\"># UDP top ports</span>\nnmap<span class=\"w\"> </span>-sU<span class=\"w\"> </span>--top-ports<span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"m\">100</span><span class=\"w\"> </span>&lt;ip&gt;\n\n<span class=\"c1\"># Combined TCP + UDP</span>\nnmap<span class=\"w\"> </span>-sS<span class=\"w\"> </span>-sU<span class=\"w\"> </span>-p<span class=\"w\"> </span>T:80,443,U:53,161<span class=\"w\"> </span>&lt;ip&gt;\n\n<span class=\"c1\"># Common UDP ports</span>\nnmap<span class=\"w\"> </span>-sU<span class=\"w\"> </span>-p<span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"m\">53</span>,67,68,69,123,161,162,500,514,623,1900,4500<span class=\"w\"> </span>&lt;ip&gt;\n</code></pre></div>\n<h2 id=\"service-version-detection\">Service &amp; Version Detection</h2>\n<div class=\"highlight\"><pre><span></span><code><span class=\"c1\"># Version detection</span>\nnmap<span class=\"w\"> </span>-sV<span class=\"w\"> </span>&lt;ip&gt;\n\n<span class=\"c1\"># Aggressive version detection (intensity 0-9)</span>\nnmap<span class=\"w\"> </span>-sV<span class=\"w\"> </span>--version-intensity<span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"m\">9</span><span class=\"w\"> </span>&lt;ip&gt;\n\n<span class=\"c1\"># Light version detection</span>\nnmap<span class=\"w\"> </span>-sV<span class=\"w\"> </span>--version-intensity<span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"m\">0</span><span class=\"w\"> </span>&lt;ip&gt;\n\n<span class=\"c1\"># Version + default scripts</span>\nnmap<span class=\"w\"> </span>-sCV<span class=\"w\"> </span>&lt;ip&gt;\n</code></pre></div>\n<h2 id=\"os-detection\">OS Detection</h2>\n<div class=\"highlight\"><pre><span></span><code><span class=\"c1\"># OS detection</span>\nnmap<span class=\"w\"> </span>-O<span class=\"w\"> </span>&lt;ip&gt;\n\n<span class=\"c1\"># Aggressive OS detection</span>\nnmap<span class=\"w\"> </span>-O<span class=\"w\"> </span>--osscan-guess<span class=\"w\"> </span>&lt;ip&gt;\n\n<span class=\"c1\"># OS + version + scripts + traceroute</span>\nnmap<span class=\"w\"> </span>-A<span class=\"w\"> </span>&lt;ip&gt;\n\n<span class=\"c1\"># Full aggressive</span>\nnmap<span class=\"w\"> </span>-A<span class=\"w\"> </span>-T4<span class=\"w\"> </span>&lt;ip&gt;\n</code></pre></div>\n<h2 id=\"script-scanning-nse\">Script Scanning (NSE)</h2>\n<div class=\"highlight\"><pre><span></span><code><span class=\"c1\"># Default scripts</span>\nnmap<span class=\"w\"> </span>-sC<span class=\"w\"> </span>&lt;ip&gt;\n\n<span class=\"c1\"># Specific script category</span>\nnmap<span class=\"w\"> </span>--script<span class=\"o\">=</span>vuln<span class=\"w\"> </span>&lt;ip&gt;\nnmap<span class=\"w\"> </span>--script<span class=\"o\">=</span>auth<span class=\"w\"> </span>&lt;ip&gt;\nnmap<span class=\"w\"> </span>--script<span class=\"o\">=</span>discovery<span class=\"w\"> </span>&lt;ip&gt;\nnmap<span class=\"w\"> </span>--script<span class=\"o\">=</span>exploit<span class=\"w\"> </span>&lt;ip&gt;\nnmap<span class=\"w\"> </span>--script<span class=\"o\">=</span>brute<span class=\"w\"> </span>&lt;ip&gt;\nnmap<span class=\"w\"> </span>--script<span class=\"o\">=</span>safe<span class=\"w\"> </span>&lt;ip&gt;\n\n<span class=\"c1\"># Multiple categories</span>\nnmap<span class=\"w\"> </span>--script<span class=\"o\">=</span><span class=\"s2\">&quot;vuln and safe&quot;</span><span class=\"w\"> </span>&lt;ip&gt;\nnmap<span class=\"w\"> </span>--script<span class=\"o\">=</span><span class=\"s2\">&quot;default or vuln&quot;</span><span class=\"w\"> </span>&lt;ip&gt;\n\n<span class=\"c1\"># Specific script</span>\nnmap<span class=\"w\"> </span>--script<span class=\"o\">=</span>http-title<span class=\"w\"> </span>&lt;ip&gt;\n\n<span class=\"c1\"># Script with arguments</span>\nnmap<span class=\"w\"> </span>--script<span class=\"o\">=</span>http-brute<span class=\"w\"> </span>--script-args<span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"nv\">userdb</span><span class=\"o\">=</span>/usr/share/wordlists/users.txt,passdb<span class=\"o\">=</span>&lt;wordlist&gt;<span class=\"w\"> </span>&lt;ip&gt;\n\n<span class=\"c1\"># List available scripts</span>\nls<span class=\"w\"> </span>/usr/share/nmap/scripts/<span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"p\">|</span><span class=\"w\"> </span>grep<span class=\"w\"> </span>smb\n</code></pre></div>\n<h2 id=\"nse-scripts-smb\">NSE Scripts — SMB</h2>\n<div class=\"highlight\"><pre><span></span><code><span class=\"c1\"># SMB enumeration suite</span>\nnmap<span class=\"w\"> </span>-p<span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"m\">445</span><span class=\"w\"> </span>--script<span class=\"o\">=</span>smb-enum-shares,smb-enum-users,smb-enum-sessions,smb-os-discovery<span class=\"w\"> </span>&lt;ip&gt;\n\n<span class=\"c1\"># SMB security mode</span>\nnmap<span class=\"w\"> </span>-p<span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"m\">445</span><span class=\"w\"> </span>--script<span class=\"o\">=</span>smb-security-mode<span class=\"w\"> </span>&lt;ip&gt;\n\n<span class=\"c1\"># SMB vulnerabilities</span>\nnmap<span class=\"w\"> </span>-p<span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"m\">445</span><span class=\"w\"> </span>--script<span class=\"o\">=</span>smb-vuln-*<span class=\"w\"> </span>&lt;ip&gt;\n\n<span class=\"c1\"># EternalBlue (MS17-010)</span>\nnmap<span class=\"w\"> </span>-p<span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"m\">445</span><span class=\"w\"> </span>--script<span class=\"o\">=</span>smb-vuln-ms17-010<span class=\"w\"> </span>&lt;ip&gt;\n\n<span class=\"c1\"># MS08-067</span>\nnmap<span class=\"w\"> </span>-p<span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"m\">445</span><span class=\"w\"> </span>--script<span class=\"o\">=</span>smb-vuln-ms08-067<span class=\"w\"> </span>&lt;ip&gt;\n\n<span class=\"c1\"># SMB brute force</span>\nnmap<span class=\"w\"> </span>-p<span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"m\">445</span><span class=\"w\"> </span>--script<span class=\"o\">=</span>smb-brute<span class=\"w\"> </span>&lt;ip&gt;\n\n<span class=\"c1\"># SMB2 support</span>\nnmap<span class=\"w\"> </span>-p<span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"m\">445</span><span class=\"w\"> </span>--script<span class=\"o\">=</span>smb2-capabilities<span class=\"w\"> </span>&lt;ip&gt;\n\n<span class=\"c1\"># Full SMB recon</span>\nnmap<span class=\"w\"> </span>-p<span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"m\">139</span>,445<span class=\"w\"> </span>--script<span class=\"o\">=</span><span class=\"s2\">&quot;smb-*&quot;</span><span class=\"w\"> </span>&lt;ip&gt;\n</code></pre></div>\n<h2 id=\"nse-scripts-http\">NSE Scripts — HTTP</h2>\n<div class=\"highlight\"><pre><span></span><code><span class=\"c1\"># HTTP info gathering</span>\nnmap<span class=\"w\"> </span>-p<span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"m\">80</span>,443,8080,8443<span class=\"w\"> </span>--script<span class=\"o\">=</span>http-title,http-server-header,http-headers<span class=\"w\"> </span>&lt;ip&gt;\n\n<span class=\"c1\"># HTTP methods</span>\nnmap<span class=\"w\"> </span>-p<span class=\"w\"> </span>&lt;port&gt;<span class=\"w\"> </span>--script<span class=\"o\">=</span>http-methods<span class=\"w\"> </span>&lt;ip&gt;\n\n<span class=\"c1\"># HTTP auth</span>\nnmap<span class=\"w\"> </span>-p<span class=\"w\"> </span>&lt;port&gt;<span class=\"w\"> </span>--script<span class=\"o\">=</span>http-auth-finder<span class=\"w\"> </span>&lt;ip&gt;\n\n<span class=\"c1\"># Web app vuln scan</span>\nnmap<span class=\"w\"> </span>-p<span class=\"w\"> </span>&lt;port&gt;<span class=\"w\"> </span>--script<span class=\"o\">=</span>http-vuln-*<span class=\"w\"> </span>&lt;ip&gt;\n\n<span class=\"c1\"># Directory brute</span>\nnmap<span class=\"w\"> </span>-p<span class=\"w\"> </span>&lt;port&gt;<span class=\"w\"> </span>--script<span class=\"o\">=</span>http-brute<span class=\"w\"> </span>&lt;ip&gt;\n\n<span class=\"c1\"># SQL injection</span>\nnmap<span class=\"w\"> </span>-p<span class=\"w\"> </span>&lt;port&gt;<span class=\"w\"> </span>--script<span class=\"o\">=</span>http-sql-injection<span class=\"w\"> </span>&lt;ip&gt;\n\n<span class=\"c1\"># XSS</span>\nnmap<span class=\"w\"> </span>-p<span class=\"w\"> </span>&lt;port&gt;<span class=\"w\"> </span>--script<span class=\"o\">=</span>http-xssed<span class=\"w\"> </span>&lt;ip&gt;\n\n<span class=\"c1\"># WordPress</span>\nnmap<span class=\"w\"> </span>-p<span class=\"w\"> </span>&lt;port&gt;<span class=\"w\"> </span>--script<span class=\"o\">=</span>http-wordpress-users,http-wordpress-enum<span class=\"w\"> </span>&lt;ip&gt;\n\n<span class=\"c1\"># HTTP enum (dirbuster-style)</span>\nnmap<span class=\"w\"> </span>-p<span class=\"w\"> </span>&lt;port&gt;<span class=\"w\"> </span>--script<span class=\"o\">=</span>http-enum<span class=\"w\"> </span>&lt;ip&gt;\n\n<span class=\"c1\"># Shellshock</span>\nnmap<span class=\"w\"> </span>-p<span class=\"w\"> </span>&lt;port&gt;<span class=\"w\"> </span>--script<span class=\"o\">=</span>http-shellshock<span class=\"w\"> </span>&lt;ip&gt;\n\n<span class=\"c1\"># robots.txt</span>\nnmap<span class=\"w\"> </span>-p<span class=\"w\"> </span>&lt;port&gt;<span class=\"w\"> </span>--script<span class=\"o\">=</span>http-robots.txt<span class=\"w\"> </span>&lt;ip&gt;\n</code></pre></div>\n<h2 id=\"nse-scripts-ftp\">NSE Scripts — FTP</h2>\n<div class=\"highlight\"><pre><span></span><code><span class=\"c1\"># FTP anonymous login</span>\nnmap<span class=\"w\"> </span>-p<span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"m\">21</span><span class=\"w\"> </span>--script<span class=\"o\">=</span>ftp-anon<span class=\"w\"> </span>&lt;ip&gt;\n\n<span class=\"c1\"># FTP bounce</span>\nnmap<span class=\"w\"> </span>-p<span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"m\">21</span><span class=\"w\"> </span>--script<span class=\"o\">=</span>ftp-bounce<span class=\"w\"> </span>&lt;ip&gt;\n\n<span class=\"c1\"># FTP brute</span>\nnmap<span class=\"w\"> </span>-p<span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"m\">21</span><span class=\"w\"> </span>--script<span class=\"o\">=</span>ftp-brute<span class=\"w\"> </span>&lt;ip&gt;\n\n<span class=\"c1\"># FTP syst</span>\nnmap<span class=\"w\"> </span>-p<span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"m\">21</span><span class=\"w\"> </span>--script<span class=\"o\">=</span>ftp-syst<span class=\"w\"> </span>&lt;ip&gt;\n\n<span class=\"c1\"># Full FTP recon</span>\nnmap<span class=\"w\"> </span>-p<span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"m\">21</span><span class=\"w\"> </span>--script<span class=\"o\">=</span><span class=\"s2\">&quot;ftp-*&quot;</span><span class=\"w\"> </span>&lt;ip&gt;\n</code></pre></div>\n<h2 id=\"nse-scripts-ssh\">NSE Scripts — SSH</h2>\n<div class=\"highlight\"><pre><span></span><code><span class=\"c1\"># SSH host keys</span>\nnmap<span class=\"w\"> </span>-p<span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"m\">22</span><span class=\"w\"> </span>--script<span class=\"o\">=</span>ssh-hostkey<span class=\"w\"> </span>&lt;ip&gt;\n\n<span class=\"c1\"># SSH auth methods</span>\nnmap<span class=\"w\"> </span>-p<span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"m\">22</span><span class=\"w\"> </span>--script<span class=\"o\">=</span>ssh-auth-methods<span class=\"w\"> </span>--script-args<span class=\"o\">=</span><span class=\"s2\">&quot;ssh.user=&lt;username&gt;&quot;</span><span class=\"w\"> </span>&lt;ip&gt;\n\n<span class=\"c1\"># SSH brute</span>\nnmap<span class=\"w\"> </span>-p<span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"m\">22</span><span class=\"w\"> </span>--script<span class=\"o\">=</span>ssh-brute<span class=\"w\"> </span>--script-args<span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"nv\">userdb</span><span class=\"o\">=</span>/usr/share/wordlists/users.txt,passdb<span class=\"o\">=</span>&lt;wordlist&gt;<span class=\"w\"> </span>&lt;ip&gt;\n\n<span class=\"c1\"># SSH2 algorithms</span>\nnmap<span class=\"w\"> </span>-p<span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"m\">22</span><span class=\"w\"> </span>--script<span class=\"o\">=</span>ssh2-enum-algos<span class=\"w\"> </span>&lt;ip&gt;\n\n<span class=\"c1\"># Known CVE check</span>\nnmap<span class=\"w\"> </span>-p<span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"m\">22</span><span class=\"w\"> </span>--script<span class=\"o\">=</span>sshv1<span class=\"w\"> </span>&lt;ip&gt;\n</code></pre></div>\n<h2 id=\"nse-scripts-mssql\">NSE Scripts — MSSQL</h2>\n<div class=\"highlight\"><pre><span></span><code><span class=\"c1\"># MSSQL info</span>\nnmap<span class=\"w\"> </span>-p<span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"m\">1433</span><span class=\"w\"> </span>--script<span class=\"o\">=</span>ms-sql-info<span class=\"w\"> </span>&lt;ip&gt;\n\n<span class=\"c1\"># MSSQL empty password</span>\nnmap<span class=\"w\"> </span>-p<span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"m\">1433</span><span class=\"w\"> </span>--script<span class=\"o\">=</span>ms-sql-empty-password<span class=\"w\"> </span>&lt;ip&gt;\n\n<span class=\"c1\"># MSSQL config</span>\nnmap<span class=\"w\"> </span>-p<span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"m\">1433</span><span class=\"w\"> </span>--script<span class=\"o\">=</span>ms-sql-config<span class=\"w\"> </span>&lt;ip&gt;\n\n<span class=\"c1\"># MSSQL query execution</span>\nnmap<span class=\"w\"> </span>-p<span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"m\">1433</span><span class=\"w\"> </span>--script<span class=\"o\">=</span>ms-sql-query<span class=\"w\"> </span>--script-args<span class=\"o\">=</span><span class=\"s2\">&quot;mssql.username=sa,mssql.password=&lt;password&gt;,ms-sql-query.query=SELECT @@version&quot;</span><span class=\"w\"> </span>&lt;ip&gt;\n\n<span class=\"c1\"># MSSQL xp_cmdshell</span>\nnmap<span class=\"w\"> </span>-p<span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"m\">1433</span><span class=\"w\"> </span>--script<span class=\"o\">=</span>ms-sql-xp-cmdshell<span class=\"w\"> </span>--script-args<span class=\"o\">=</span><span class=\"s2\">&quot;mssql.username=sa,mssql.password=&lt;password&gt;,ms-sql-xp-cmdshell.cmd=whoami&quot;</span><span class=\"w\"> </span>&lt;ip&gt;\n\n<span class=\"c1\"># MSSQL brute</span>\nnmap<span class=\"w\"> </span>-p<span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"m\">1433</span><span class=\"w\"> </span>--script<span class=\"o\">=</span>ms-sql-brute<span class=\"w\"> </span>&lt;ip&gt;\n\n<span class=\"c1\"># Full MSSQL</span>\nnmap<span class=\"w\"> </span>-p<span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"m\">1433</span><span class=\"w\"> </span>--script<span class=\"o\">=</span><span class=\"s2\">&quot;ms-sql-*&quot;</span><span class=\"w\"> </span>--script-args<span class=\"o\">=</span><span class=\"s2\">&quot;mssql.username=sa,mssql.password=&lt;password&gt;&quot;</span><span class=\"w\"> </span>&lt;ip&gt;\n</code></pre></div>\n<h2 id=\"nse-scripts-snmp\">NSE Scripts — SNMP</h2>\n<div class=\"highlight\"><pre><span></span><code><span class=\"c1\"># SNMP info</span>\nnmap<span class=\"w\"> </span>-sU<span class=\"w\"> </span>-p<span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"m\">161</span><span class=\"w\"> </span>--script<span class=\"o\">=</span>snmp-info<span class=\"w\"> </span>&lt;ip&gt;\n\n<span class=\"c1\"># SNMP system description</span>\nnmap<span class=\"w\"> </span>-sU<span class=\"w\"> </span>-p<span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"m\">161</span><span class=\"w\"> </span>--script<span class=\"o\">=</span>snmp-sysdescr<span class=\"w\"> </span>&lt;ip&gt;\n\n<span class=\"c1\"># SNMP interfaces</span>\nnmap<span class=\"w\"> </span>-sU<span class=\"w\"> </span>-p<span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"m\">161</span><span class=\"w\"> </span>--script<span class=\"o\">=</span>snmp-interfaces<span class=\"w\"> </span>&lt;ip&gt;\n\n<span class=\"c1\"># SNMP processes</span>\nnmap<span class=\"w\"> </span>-sU<span class=\"w\"> </span>-p<span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"m\">161</span><span class=\"w\"> </span>--script<span class=\"o\">=</span>snmp-processes<span class=\"w\"> </span>&lt;ip&gt;\n\n<span class=\"c1\"># SNMP Windows users</span>\nnmap<span class=\"w\"> </span>-sU<span class=\"w\"> </span>-p<span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"m\">161</span><span class=\"w\"> </span>--script<span class=\"o\">=</span>snmp-win32-users<span class=\"w\"> </span>&lt;ip&gt;\n\n<span class=\"c1\"># SNMP Windows services</span>\nnmap<span class=\"w\"> </span>-sU<span class=\"w\"> </span>-p<span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"m\">161</span><span class=\"w\"> </span>--script<span class=\"o\">=</span>snmp-win32-services<span class=\"w\"> </span>&lt;ip&gt;\n\n<span class=\"c1\"># SNMP brute community string</span>\nnmap<span class=\"w\"> </span>-sU<span class=\"w\"> </span>-p<span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"m\">161</span><span class=\"w\"> </span>--script<span class=\"o\">=</span>snmp-brute<span class=\"w\"> </span>&lt;ip&gt;\n\n<span class=\"c1\"># Full SNMP</span>\nnmap<span class=\"w\"> </span>-sU<span class=\"w\"> </span>-p<span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"m\">161</span><span class=\"w\"> </span>--script<span class=\"o\">=</span><span class=\"s2\">&quot;snmp-*&quot;</span><span class=\"w\"> </span>&lt;ip&gt;\n</code></pre></div>\n<h2 id=\"nse-scripts-rdp\">NSE Scripts — RDP</h2>\n<div class=\"highlight\"><pre><span></span><code><span class=\"c1\"># RDP info</span>\nnmap<span class=\"w\"> </span>-p<span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"m\">3389</span><span class=\"w\"> </span>--script<span class=\"o\">=</span>rdp-enum-encryption<span class=\"w\"> </span>&lt;ip&gt;\n\n<span class=\"c1\"># RDP vuln check (BlueKeep)</span>\nnmap<span class=\"w\"> </span>-p<span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"m\">3389</span><span class=\"w\"> </span>--script<span class=\"o\">=</span>rdp-vuln-ms12-020<span class=\"w\"> </span>&lt;ip&gt;\n\n<span class=\"c1\"># NLA check</span>\nnmap<span class=\"w\"> </span>-p<span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"m\">3389</span><span class=\"w\"> </span>--script<span class=\"o\">=</span>rdp-enum-encryption<span class=\"w\"> </span>&lt;ip&gt;\n</code></pre></div>\n<h2 id=\"nse-scripts-other-services\">NSE Scripts — Other Services</h2>\n<div class=\"highlight\"><pre><span></span><code><span class=\"c1\"># MySQL</span>\nnmap<span class=\"w\"> </span>-p<span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"m\">3306</span><span class=\"w\"> </span>--script<span class=\"o\">=</span>mysql-info,mysql-empty-password,mysql-brute<span class=\"w\"> </span>&lt;ip&gt;\n\n<span class=\"c1\"># PostgreSQL</span>\nnmap<span class=\"w\"> </span>-p<span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"m\">5432</span><span class=\"w\"> </span>--script<span class=\"o\">=</span>pgsql-brute<span class=\"w\"> </span>&lt;ip&gt;\n\n<span class=\"c1\"># MongoDB</span>\nnmap<span class=\"w\"> </span>-p<span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"m\">27017</span><span class=\"w\"> </span>--script<span class=\"o\">=</span>mongodb-info,mongodb-databases<span class=\"w\"> </span>&lt;ip&gt;\n\n<span class=\"c1\"># Redis</span>\nnmap<span class=\"w\"> </span>-p<span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"m\">6379</span><span class=\"w\"> </span>--script<span class=\"o\">=</span>redis-info<span class=\"w\"> </span>&lt;ip&gt;\n\n<span class=\"c1\"># Memcached</span>\nnmap<span class=\"w\"> </span>-p<span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"m\">11211</span><span class=\"w\"> </span>--script<span class=\"o\">=</span>memcached-info<span class=\"w\"> </span>&lt;ip&gt;\n\n<span class=\"c1\"># LDAP</span>\nnmap<span class=\"w\"> </span>-p<span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"m\">389</span>,636<span class=\"w\"> </span>--script<span class=\"o\">=</span>ldap-rootdse,ldap-search<span class=\"w\"> </span>&lt;ip&gt;\n\n<span class=\"c1\"># DNS</span>\nnmap<span class=\"w\"> </span>-p<span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"m\">53</span><span class=\"w\"> </span>--script<span class=\"o\">=</span>dns-zone-transfer<span class=\"w\"> </span>--script-args<span class=\"o\">=</span><span class=\"s2\">&quot;dns-zone-transfer.domain=&lt;domain&gt;&quot;</span><span class=\"w\"> </span>&lt;ip&gt;\n\n<span class=\"c1\"># SMTP</span>\nnmap<span class=\"w\"> </span>-p<span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"m\">25</span>,587<span class=\"w\"> </span>--script<span class=\"o\">=</span>smtp-commands,smtp-enum-users,smtp-open-relay<span class=\"w\"> </span>&lt;ip&gt;\n\n<span class=\"c1\"># POP3/IMAP</span>\nnmap<span class=\"w\"> </span>-p<span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"m\">110</span>,143,993,995<span class=\"w\"> </span>--script<span class=\"o\">=</span>pop3-capabilities,imap-capabilities<span class=\"w\"> </span>&lt;ip&gt;\n\n<span class=\"c1\"># VNC</span>\nnmap<span class=\"w\"> </span>-p<span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"m\">5900</span><span class=\"w\"> </span>--script<span class=\"o\">=</span>vnc-info,vnc-brute,realvnc-auth-bypass<span class=\"w\"> </span>&lt;ip&gt;\n\n<span class=\"c1\"># NFS</span>\nnmap<span class=\"w\"> </span>-p<span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"m\">111</span>,2049<span class=\"w\"> </span>--script<span class=\"o\">=</span>nfs-ls,nfs-showmount,nfs-statfs<span class=\"w\"> </span>&lt;ip&gt;\n\n<span class=\"c1\"># Telnet</span>\nnmap<span class=\"w\"> </span>-p<span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"m\">23</span><span class=\"w\"> </span>--script<span class=\"o\">=</span>telnet-ntlm-info<span class=\"w\"> </span>&lt;ip&gt;\n</code></pre></div>\n<h2 id=\"timing-templates\">Timing Templates</h2>\n<div class=\"highlight\"><pre><span></span><code><span class=\"c1\"># T0 - paranoid (IDS evasion)</span>\nnmap<span class=\"w\"> </span>-T0<span class=\"w\"> </span>&lt;ip&gt;\n\n<span class=\"c1\"># T1 - sneaky</span>\nnmap<span class=\"w\"> </span>-T1<span class=\"w\"> </span>&lt;ip&gt;\n\n<span class=\"c1\"># T2 - polite</span>\nnmap<span class=\"w\"> </span>-T2<span class=\"w\"> </span>&lt;ip&gt;\n\n<span class=\"c1\"># T3 - normal (default)</span>\nnmap<span class=\"w\"> </span>-T3<span class=\"w\"> </span>&lt;ip&gt;\n\n<span class=\"c1\"># T4 - aggressive (recommended for CTF/HTB)</span>\nnmap<span class=\"w\"> </span>-T4<span class=\"w\"> </span>&lt;ip&gt;\n\n<span class=\"c1\"># T5 - insane</span>\nnmap<span class=\"w\"> </span>-T5<span class=\"w\"> </span>&lt;ip&gt;\n\n<span class=\"c1\"># Manual timing control</span>\nnmap<span class=\"w\"> </span>--min-rate<span class=\"o\">=</span><span class=\"m\">1000</span><span class=\"w\"> </span>--max-rate<span class=\"o\">=</span><span class=\"m\">5000</span><span class=\"w\"> </span>&lt;ip&gt;\nnmap<span class=\"w\"> </span>--min-parallelism<span class=\"o\">=</span><span class=\"m\">50</span><span class=\"w\"> </span>--max-parallelism<span class=\"o\">=</span><span class=\"m\">200</span><span class=\"w\"> </span>&lt;ip&gt;\nnmap<span class=\"w\"> </span>--scan-delay<span class=\"o\">=</span>100ms<span class=\"w\"> </span>&lt;ip&gt;\nnmap<span class=\"w\"> </span>--max-retries<span class=\"o\">=</span><span class=\"m\">2</span><span class=\"w\"> </span>&lt;ip&gt;\n</code></pre></div>\n<h2 id=\"output-formats\">Output Formats</h2>\n<div class=\"highlight\"><pre><span></span><code><span class=\"c1\"># Normal output</span>\nnmap<span class=\"w\"> </span>-oN<span class=\"w\"> </span>scan.txt<span class=\"w\"> </span>&lt;ip&gt;\n\n<span class=\"c1\"># Grepable output</span>\nnmap<span class=\"w\"> </span>-oG<span class=\"w\"> </span>scan.gnmap<span class=\"w\"> </span>&lt;ip&gt;\n\n<span class=\"c1\"># XML output</span>\nnmap<span class=\"w\"> </span>-oX<span class=\"w\"> </span>scan.xml<span class=\"w\"> </span>&lt;ip&gt;\n\n<span class=\"c1\"># All formats at once</span>\nnmap<span class=\"w\"> </span>-oA<span class=\"w\"> </span>scan<span class=\"w\"> </span>&lt;ip&gt;\n\n<span class=\"c1\"># Append to existing file</span>\nnmap<span class=\"w\"> </span>-oN<span class=\"w\"> </span>-<span class=\"w\"> </span>--append-output<span class=\"w\"> </span>&lt;ip&gt;<span class=\"w\"> </span>&gt;&gt;<span class=\"w\"> </span>scan.txt\n\n<span class=\"c1\"># Script kiddie output (leet speak)</span>\nnmap<span class=\"w\"> </span>-oS<span class=\"w\"> </span>scan.txt<span class=\"w\"> </span>&lt;ip&gt;\n\n<span class=\"c1\"># Verbose output</span>\nnmap<span class=\"w\"> </span>-v<span class=\"w\"> </span>&lt;ip&gt;\nnmap<span class=\"w\"> </span>-vv<span class=\"w\"> </span>&lt;ip&gt;\n\n<span class=\"c1\"># Debug output</span>\nnmap<span class=\"w\"> </span>-d<span class=\"w\"> </span>&lt;ip&gt;\nnmap<span class=\"w\"> </span>--packet-trace<span class=\"w\"> </span>&lt;ip&gt;\n</code></pre></div>\n<h2 id=\"firewall-evasion\">Firewall Evasion</h2>\n<div class=\"highlight\"><pre><span></span><code><span class=\"c1\"># Fragment packets (8 bytes per fragment)</span>\nnmap<span class=\"w\"> </span>-f<span class=\"w\"> </span>&lt;ip&gt;\n\n<span class=\"c1\"># Double fragmentation (16 bytes)</span>\nnmap<span class=\"w\"> </span>-ff<span class=\"w\"> </span>&lt;ip&gt;\n\n<span class=\"c1\"># Custom MTU</span>\nnmap<span class=\"w\"> </span>--mtu<span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"m\">24</span><span class=\"w\"> </span>&lt;ip&gt;\n\n<span class=\"c1\"># Decoy scan (use fake source IPs)</span>\nnmap<span class=\"w\"> </span>-D<span class=\"w\"> </span>RND:10<span class=\"w\"> </span>&lt;ip&gt;\nnmap<span class=\"w\"> </span>-D<span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"m\">192</span>.168.1.5,192.168.1.10,ME<span class=\"w\"> </span>&lt;ip&gt;\n\n<span class=\"c1\"># Source port spoofing (bypass firewall rules allowing 53/80)</span>\nnmap<span class=\"w\"> </span>--source-port<span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"m\">53</span><span class=\"w\"> </span>&lt;ip&gt;\nnmap<span class=\"w\"> </span>-g<span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"m\">80</span><span class=\"w\"> </span>&lt;ip&gt;\n\n<span class=\"c1\"># Custom TTL</span>\nnmap<span class=\"w\"> </span>--ttl<span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"m\">64</span><span class=\"w\"> </span>&lt;ip&gt;\n\n<span class=\"c1\"># Spoof MAC address</span>\nnmap<span class=\"w\"> </span>--spoof-mac<span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"m\">0</span><span class=\"w\"> </span>&lt;ip&gt;<span class=\"w\">        </span><span class=\"c1\"># random MAC</span>\nnmap<span class=\"w\"> </span>--spoof-mac<span class=\"w\"> </span>Cisco<span class=\"w\"> </span>&lt;ip&gt;<span class=\"w\">    </span><span class=\"c1\"># vendor prefix</span>\n\n<span class=\"c1\"># Randomize target order</span>\nnmap<span class=\"w\"> </span>--randomize-hosts<span class=\"w\"> </span>&lt;ip&gt;/24\n\n<span class=\"c1\"># Bad checksum (evade some IDS)</span>\nnmap<span class=\"w\"> </span>--badsum<span class=\"w\"> </span>&lt;ip&gt;\n\n<span class=\"c1\"># Idle scan (zombie host)</span>\nnmap<span class=\"w\"> </span>-sI<span class=\"w\"> </span>&lt;zombie_ip&gt;<span class=\"w\"> </span>&lt;ip&gt;\n\n<span class=\"c1\"># Slow scan with fragmentation</span>\nnmap<span class=\"w\"> </span>-T1<span class=\"w\"> </span>-f<span class=\"w\"> </span>--source-port<span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"m\">53</span><span class=\"w\"> </span>&lt;ip&gt;\n</code></pre></div>\n<h2 id=\"parsing-with-grepawk\">Parsing with grep/awk</h2>\n<div class=\"highlight\"><pre><span></span><code><span class=\"c1\"># Extract open ports from grepable output</span>\ngrep<span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"s2\">&quot;open&quot;</span><span class=\"w\"> </span>scan.gnmap<span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"p\">|</span><span class=\"w\"> </span>awk<span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"s1\">&#39;{print $5}&#39;</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"p\">|</span><span class=\"w\"> </span>cut<span class=\"w\"> </span>-d<span class=\"s1\">&#39;/&#39;</span><span class=\"w\"> </span>-f1\n\n<span class=\"c1\"># One-liner: extract just open port numbers</span>\nnmap<span class=\"w\"> </span>-p-<span class=\"w\"> </span>-oG<span class=\"w\"> </span>-<span class=\"w\"> </span>&lt;ip&gt;<span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"p\">|</span><span class=\"w\"> </span>grep<span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"s2\">&quot;open&quot;</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"p\">|</span><span class=\"w\"> </span>grep<span class=\"w\"> </span>-oP<span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"s1\">&#39;\\d+(?=/open)&#39;</span>\n\n<span class=\"c1\"># Extract hosts with specific port open</span>\ngrep<span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"s2\">&quot;445/open&quot;</span><span class=\"w\"> </span>scan.gnmap<span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"p\">|</span><span class=\"w\"> </span>awk<span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"s1\">&#39;{print $2}&#39;</span>\n\n<span class=\"c1\"># Parse XML with xmllint</span>\nxmllint<span class=\"w\"> </span>--xpath<span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"s2\">&quot;//port[@state=&#39;open&#39;]&quot;</span><span class=\"w\"> </span>scan.xml\n\n<span class=\"c1\"># Extract all IPs from subnet scan</span>\nnmap<span class=\"w\"> </span>-sn<span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"m\">192</span>.168.1.0/24<span class=\"w\"> </span>-oG<span class=\"w\"> </span>-<span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"p\">|</span><span class=\"w\"> </span>grep<span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"s2\">&quot;Up&quot;</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"p\">|</span><span class=\"w\"> </span>awk<span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"s1\">&#39;{print $2}&#39;</span>\n\n<span class=\"c1\"># One-liner full scan + grep for open ports</span>\nnmap<span class=\"w\"> </span>-sCV<span class=\"w\"> </span>-T4<span class=\"w\"> </span>-p-<span class=\"w\"> </span>&lt;ip&gt;<span class=\"w\"> </span>-oG<span class=\"w\"> </span>-<span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"p\">|</span><span class=\"w\"> </span>grep<span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"s2\">&quot;open&quot;</span>\n\n<span class=\"c1\"># Extract services from normal output</span>\ngrep<span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"s2\">&quot;open&quot;</span><span class=\"w\"> </span>scan.txt<span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"p\">|</span><span class=\"w\"> </span>awk<span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"s1\">&#39;{print $1, $3}&#39;</span>\n\n<span class=\"c1\"># Port list for use with other tools</span>\nnmap<span class=\"w\"> </span>-p-<span class=\"w\"> </span>&lt;ip&gt;<span class=\"w\"> </span>-oG<span class=\"w\"> </span>-<span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"p\">|</span><span class=\"w\"> </span>grep<span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"s2\">&quot;open&quot;</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"p\">|</span><span class=\"w\"> </span>grep<span class=\"w\"> </span>-oP<span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"s1\">&#39;\\d+(?=/open)&#39;</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"p\">|</span><span class=\"w\"> </span>tr<span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"s1\">&#39;\\n&#39;</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"s1\">&#39;,&#39;</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"p\">|</span><span class=\"w\"> </span>sed<span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"s1\">&#39;s/,$//&#39;</span>\n\n<span class=\"c1\"># Find hosts with RDP open across subnet</span>\nnmap<span class=\"w\"> </span>-p<span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"m\">3389</span><span class=\"w\"> </span>-oG<span class=\"w\"> </span>-<span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"m\">192</span>.168.1.0/24<span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"p\">|</span><span class=\"w\"> </span>grep<span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"s2\">&quot;3389/open&quot;</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"p\">|</span><span class=\"w\"> </span>awk<span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"s1\">&#39;{print $2}&#39;</span>\n\n<span class=\"c1\"># Extract version strings</span>\ngrep<span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"s2\">&quot;VERSION&quot;</span><span class=\"w\"> </span>scan.txt\ngrep<span class=\"w\"> </span>-oP<span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"s1\">&#39;(?&lt;=\\()\\S+(?=\\))&#39;</span><span class=\"w\"> </span>scan.txt\n</code></pre></div>\n<h2 id=\"common-compound-commands\">Common Compound Commands</h2>\n<div class=\"highlight\"><pre><span></span><code><span class=\"c1\"># HTB/CTF quick win</span>\nnmap<span class=\"w\"> </span>-sCV<span class=\"w\"> </span>-T4<span class=\"w\"> </span>--min-rate<span class=\"o\">=</span><span class=\"m\">1000</span><span class=\"w\"> </span>-p-<span class=\"w\"> </span>&lt;ip&gt;<span class=\"w\"> </span>-oA<span class=\"w\"> </span>/tmp/nmap_&lt;ip&gt;\n\n<span class=\"c1\"># Full recon with all scripts on discovered ports</span>\n<span class=\"nv\">ports</span><span class=\"o\">=</span><span class=\"k\">$(</span>nmap<span class=\"w\"> </span>-p-<span class=\"w\"> </span>--min-rate<span class=\"o\">=</span><span class=\"m\">5000</span><span class=\"w\"> </span>-T4<span class=\"w\"> </span>&lt;ip&gt;<span class=\"w\"> </span>-oG<span class=\"w\"> </span>-<span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"p\">|</span><span class=\"w\"> </span>grep<span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"s2\">&quot;open&quot;</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"p\">|</span><span class=\"w\"> </span>grep<span class=\"w\"> </span>-oP<span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"s1\">&#39;\\d+(?=/open)&#39;</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"p\">|</span><span class=\"w\"> </span>tr<span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"s1\">&#39;\\n&#39;</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"s1\">&#39;,&#39;</span><span class=\"k\">)</span>\nnmap<span class=\"w\"> </span>-sCV<span class=\"w\"> </span>-p<span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"nv\">$ports</span><span class=\"w\"> </span>&lt;ip&gt;\n\n<span class=\"c1\"># Vuln scan on web ports</span>\nnmap<span class=\"w\"> </span>-p<span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"m\">80</span>,443,8080,8443<span class=\"w\"> </span>--script<span class=\"o\">=</span><span class=\"s2\">&quot;http-* and vuln&quot;</span><span class=\"w\"> </span>&lt;ip&gt;\n\n<span class=\"c1\"># Domain controller full recon</span>\nnmap<span class=\"w\"> </span>-sCV<span class=\"w\"> </span>-p<span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"m\">53</span>,88,135,139,389,445,464,593,636,3268,3269,3389,5985,9389<span class=\"w\"> </span>&lt;ip&gt;\n\n<span class=\"c1\"># Linux box full recon</span>\nnmap<span class=\"w\"> </span>-sCV<span class=\"w\"> </span>-p<span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"m\">21</span>,22,25,53,80,110,111,143,443,445,2049,3306,5432,6379,8080<span class=\"w\"> </span>&lt;ip&gt;\n</code></pre></div>", "excerpt": "Nmap Host Discovery # Ping sweep (no port scan) nmap -sn 192 .168.1.0/24 # ARP discovery (local network, requires root) nmap -PR -sn 192 .168.1.0/24 # TCP SYN ping nmap -PS22,80,443 -sn &lt;ip&gt; # U", "tags": []}